        "ggsF1YT33ER_text": "<p>Advertorial</p>",
        "ggqdEjBWiOz_text": "Thousands Are Upgrading to This Blanket – Is It Really That Good?",
        "ggUJT5n4JrT_text": "<p>Let’s get one thing straight: there’s no shortage of blankets out there. You can walk into any store and pick up a “soft” throw for a few bucks. <strong>So why is this particular fleece blanket causing such a stir?</strong><br><br>Social media posts are calling it <i><strong>“The reason I keep cancelling plans.”</strong></i><strong> </strong>People claim it’s so soft, so cozy, that it’s turning movie nights into unforgettable experiences. Others say they’re gifting it to everyone they know. But can one blanket really deliver on that level of comfort, or is it just clever marketing?<br><br><strong>As someone who has a closet full of mediocre throws, I had my doubts.</strong></p>",
        "gg9pEhWcRGT_text": "<p><span style=\"font-size:14px;\"><i>Crafted by the Swiss brand The Fleece Company, currently taking social media by storm</i></span></p>",
        "ggcG-rClrPn_text": "<strong>What Makes This Blanket Unlike Any Other?</strong>",
        "ggexbcGUJ7w_text": "<p>First, let’s talk about what sets this blanket apart. It’s marketed as “the coziest blanket you’ll ever own,” with claims of unmatched softness, incredible warmth, and luxurious quality. The company behind it says it’s designed with advanced materials to keep you warm without overheating, all while being lightweight and breathable.</p>",
        "ggQUtpalAyq_text": "<p>\"This blanket made me cancel plans...\"</p>",
        "ggZez4m9rL6_text": "<p>Last Friday, I was supposed to go out with friends. But as I was getting ready, I made the mistake of sitting down with this blanket for \"just a minute.\" Two hours later, I was still wrapped up, binge-watching my favorite show, and texting my friends with an \"I’m not feeling great\" excuse.</p>",
        "ggYD-6DWJ30_text": "<p>-Alisa G.</p>",
        "ggQX2x4aXlp_childItem_0": "<p>Verified Customer</p>"
      }
    },
